                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9992" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0442</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">678 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">虚实协同聚动能：延长石油销售公司变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Virtual-real Synergy Promoting Change: Yanchang Petroleum Sales Company’s Organizational Evolution Road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谭乐，李纯青（通讯作者），李梦雯，何玉明，蒿坡，孟云娇，洪嘉琪，张文明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">延长石油销售公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革；国有企业；市场化改革；数字化转型；产品经理虚拟组织；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Organizational Change; State-owned Enterprise; state-owned enterprises; Market-oriented Reform; Digital Transformation; Virtual Organization of Product Managers</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">延长石油销售公司作为国有能源化工企业，在面临油品行业从“卖方市场”转为“买方市场”以及“加快推进国有企业数字化转型”双重驱动下，面临市场化转型及数字化转型“两化融合”的双重挑战。本案例描述了延长石油销售公司的两次关键变革实践——“市场化”改革和“数字化”新变革。具体来说，案例首先描述延长石油销售公司如何在市场化转型背景下，在能源销售行业激烈竞争中，通过“市场化”改革，实现“自主定价”赢得大“实”效。进而聚焦数字化转型背景下，通过建立“数字化产品经理虚拟组织”另辟蹊径应对国企数字化转型痛点问题，盘活内部人才资源，全面提升企业管理水平和竞争力的“数字化”变革过程；以及变革过程中如何通过党建引领、文化、管理机制赋能促进变革成功。本案例基于同一企业经历的两次典型性变革实践，可通过对比性分析帮助学生理解掌握组织变革相关理论，也可为其他国有企业在“两化融合”背景下进行组织变革，成功进行市场化转型及数字化转型促高质量发展培育新质生产力提供重要借鉴与启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a state-owned energy and chemical enterprise, Yanchang Petroleum Sales Company is faced with the dual drives of (1) the transformation of the oil industry from a &quot;seller&#39;s market&quot; to a &quot;buyer&#39;s market&quot; and (2) the “accelerated digital transformation of state-owned enterprises&quot;, which compromise the integrated challenges of the company. This case depicts two crucial transformation practices of Yanchang Petroleum Sales Company including marketization reform and digitization transformation. Specifically, the present case describes (1) how Yanchang Petroleum Sale Company achieved &quot;independent pricing&quot; to win &quot;big benefits&quot; through &quot;marketization&quot; reforms and (2) the &quot;digitalization&quot; reforms in the context of digital transformation through the establishment of a &quot;virtual organization of product managers&quot; to find a new way to deal with the key problems of the digital transformation of state-owned enterprises, revitalizing internal human resources, and comprehensively improving the process of enterprise management and competitiveness; as well as how to promote the success of the change through party building leadership, culture, and management mechanism empowerment in the process of organizational change. This case is grounded in two exemplary transformation practices undergone by the same enterprise. By comparative analysis, this case can help students understand and master theories associated with organizational change and can also provide important reference and insights for other state-owned enterprises to carry out organizational change in the context of &quot;integration of marketization and digitalization &quot;, thus successfully carrying out market-oriented transformation and digital transformation to promote high-quality development and new quality productivity.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革；数字化转型变革；虚拟组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
